   [$Mr. (^Sheriffe,^) $] Indeed his Business I did not know; but he #
was at our House about the
middle of (^February^) , it was thereabouts.
   [$ (^L. C. J.^) $] When was it? what (^February^) ?               #
   [$Mr. (^Sheriffe,^) $] The last (^February^) .
